OL,3,C'Bespoke' school uniform items to be
OL,4,Climited at Government schools
OL,6,FJersey's Education Minister has
OL,7,Fapproved plans to limit the number of
OL,8,Fbespoke uniform items at government
OL,9,Fschools.
OL,11,FBespoke items will be capped at five
OL,12,Fper child - including PE kit.
OL,14,FFree clothing provided to students is
OL,15,Fnot included in this number.
OL,17,FThe changes come after a report in
OL,18,FApril concluded that uniform costs
OL,19,Fcould be reduced with fewer branded
OL,20,Fand compulsory items - with 40% of
OL,21,Funiforms made-up of such items.
